title: AAPL down ahead of Apple’s Q4 2015 earnings call tomorrow
text: AAPL is down significantly today ahead of Apple’s fiscal Q4 earnings call scheduled to take place tomorrow, despite the usual predictions of growth across the board by the market and the majority of analysts.
